These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, country, jazz, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, badminton, golf, volleyball
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, horse, rabbit
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, canasta, domino
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 7. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1
 8. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 9. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
10. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person playing monopoly and the fan of blues##7
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
13. the person playing domino is the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | country | jazz    | blues   |
| Sport   | baseball | golf | badminton | volleyball |
| Pet           | dog       | horse   | rabbit  | cat     |
| Game     | monopoly      | canasta   | domino    | chess    |

