.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, mango, onion, watermelon
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, turquise, blood-red, red
4 different pets are kept: rat, lizard, frog, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, ice-hockey, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 3. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 4. the person who's sport is volleyball is the owner of the rat##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 6. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the right of the person eating onion##5
 7. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the owner of the rat##7
 8. the person eating apricot is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
10. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
11. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | apricot   | onion       | watermelon    | mango      |
| Color   | grey | red | turquise         | blood-red   |
| Pet   | hedgehog   | rat  | lizard       | frog |
| Sport         | golf      | volleyball  | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

