.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, reggae, house, soul
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, martial-arts, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dunhill, baccarat, bongani
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, lizard
 1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the fan of reggae is the dunhill-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the fan of house is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the fan of soul##6
 9. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the baccarat-smoker is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Music-Genre           | soul | techno | reggae | house |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | zombie    | crime    | martial-arts    |
| Cigar   | fonseca        | bongani   | dunhill   | baccarat         |
| Pet           | goat          | dog       | lizard   | horse           |

