 4. the person drinking sprite is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person driving the train is not the person watching crime movies##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the train##7
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
11. the person playing scrabble is not the person watching crime movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | soy-milk       | mirinda         | sprite       |
| Transport         | train     | airplane    | roller   | car |
