 7. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to new-york is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the trike##7
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
11. the person watching adventure movies is the person traveling to new-york##1
12. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person eating spinach##7
13. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
