 8. the wooden house is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| House         | craftsman      | townhouse   | wooden   | art-deco       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| City   | prague  | edinburgh | marseilles   | rome     |
| Sport         | baseball   | soccer    | rowing   | skateboarding |

