.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, apricot, red, lilac
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, lemon, pear
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, oliveros, vegafina
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
 1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person eating apricot##5
 3. the vegafina-smoker is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating lemon##5
 7. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person who likes turquise and the person eating pear##7
 8. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
10. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the person who likes turquise is the person eating lemon##1
12. the person eating lemon is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | apricot   | lilac     | red   | turquise |
| Food       | pear   | apricot | artichoke | lemon    |
| Cigar      | oliveros | vegafina | blend   | alhambra  |
| Pet        | rabbit | cat     | hamster   | goldfish |

