 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
 5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is not the police-officer##6
 7. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 8. the person driving the bike is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 9. the writer is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
10. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person driving the van##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person traveling to berlin##6
13. the police-officer is on the left of the writer##1
