.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, hiking, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, trike, snowmobile
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
4 different games are played: whist, canasta, domino, poker
 1. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
 2. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person playing canasta is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person driving the trike and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person playing whist##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
12. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | singing      | hiking     | cooking   | baking    |
| Transport     | snowmobile | trike   | motorbike | van |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Game   | canasta       | poker | whist   | domino    |

 